Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.50,0:00:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到本厨艺竞技场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.40,0:00:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出场吧 两位可爱的围裙斗士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.40,0:00:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚请诸位在竞技场上尽情地展现自己的料理才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.20,0:00:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别做出奇怪的玩意儿啊 椰丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能输给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.80,0:00:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢 竟敢向我挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.40,0:00:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,势必将你打垮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.10,0:00:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气死我也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.90,0:00:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.50,0:00:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次的食材 任由你们煎炸烹煮都OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.40,0:00:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是从头至尾没有一丝多余之处的完美蔬菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.10,0:00:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字就是——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.40,0:00:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大萝卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.10,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大大大大大萝卜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.80,0:01:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 就算是暑假 也不能总睡懒觉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.52,0:02:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(352,270)\fs28\1c&bb0000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\bord2}椰丝之夏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个 接下来要去哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.70,0:02:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烤鱿鱼真的是很好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,融身于喧嚣之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自然地静下心来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.90,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的杂音消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,静寂的世界降临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.70,0:03:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何外人 只属于我的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 静香 我推荐的戏剧不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.30,0:03:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我是第一次看独角戏 不过好感动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为寻找死别的父亲的身影而踏上旅途的女主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.70,0:03:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在旅途中与人们的相遇和离别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后在最后一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.10,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远走下去 走我所选择的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.00,0:03:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素…素奈绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 素奈绪你可真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.20,0:04:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这股涌上心头的感动要如何平息啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了 我要在暑假里练习这场戏 然后自己来出演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成之后你要来看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你再次感动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同笨蛋一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.80,0:04:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟会如此热衷于一件小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不出那么孩子气的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找碴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.10,0:04:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等下 大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞了人连句道歉的话都没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞人的是你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.40,0:04:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有必要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.30,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小瞧我们松笠连合吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我打扁你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.80,0:05:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来 你们很欠缺教育啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道是…铁乙女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万物 剑风所至皆粉碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱群蝶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.60,0:05:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饶命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.00,0:05:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模仿铁学姐确实效果显著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是龙鸣馆学生会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椰子和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别多管闲事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.20,0:05:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那群家伙我一人便足以应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就那么想出风头吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.30,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人已经回来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.00,0:06:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和美 妈妈有重要的事情要跟你说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.70,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.80,0:07:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能正式排练了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.40,0:07:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 那出令人感动的舞台剧 即使是我也能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便说说的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近卫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是跟以前一样很喜欢戏剧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.80,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是暑假 为什么你还要故意出现在我面前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.80,0:07:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你为什么总要和我过不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你问为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是片令人心情愉悦的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 然后是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.70,0:08:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班级发表会的主角就定为素奈绪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.70,0:08:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素奈绪的妈妈是演员吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以演戏对你而言很简单吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.70,0:08:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.40,0:08:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会演戏啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:33.50,Default,,0000,-480,0320,,森林的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:33.50,Default,,0000,-480,0287,,公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:33.50,Default,,0000,-480,0255,,近卫素奈绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷奥同学 你都看见了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素奈绪你好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让我继续看下去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对马是个大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和美等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:09:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭的话 你们两个人去吃不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.20,0:09:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望和美能对我多加深了解啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们三人先坐下来谈一谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这与我无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.40,0:09:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 我已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.70,0:09:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.60,0:09:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 请再听我说一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 好过份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别把我当傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.50,0:10:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会永远是个小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别说这么失礼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.50,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶…下面的台词是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经结束了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会觉得害臊吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.80,0:10:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自言自语地念着一堆莫明其妙的台词
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这叫做独角戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然尚在练习中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.00,0:10:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成之后就会引发感人的风暴啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真让人不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你 我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.80,0:10:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.60,0:10:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2-A的近卫素奈绪学姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 难道我很有名？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.00,0:10:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.10,0:11:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了创建戏剧部而向学生会长宣战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.50,0:11:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后一直失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.90,0:11:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 近卫学姐还真是孩子气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.30,0:11:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热衷于一件事 如同笨蛋一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像个笨蛋又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戏剧是我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.80,0:11:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.30,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会永远是个小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别说这么失礼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.70,0:11:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,融身于喧嚣之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自然地静下心来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的杂音消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,静寂的世界降临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.30,0:14:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何外人 只属于我的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.10,0:14:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.80,0:14:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你看啊 是大海啊 大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为海的那一边有什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 我想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖精的国度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有的话就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里空无一物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何 和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.70,0:15:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.60,0:15:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.80,0:15:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.80,0:15:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸做的饭菜为什么会这样好吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.10,0:15:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那还用问 当然是为了让和美与妈妈都高兴啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我长大了也会让爸爸高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.50,0:15:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力练习 像爸爸那样能烧一手好菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.80,0:15:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我很期待哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.10,0:15:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那曾是我的梦想 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.40,0:15:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦想已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.50,0:16:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我间的回忆 宛如刺入胸膛的美丽荆刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.50,0:16:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又酸又甜 紧紧缠绕我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.70,0:16:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这份痛楚 要持续到何时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近卫学姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.50,0:16:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍然难以接受 你已不在人世的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.30,0:16:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我说着“我回来了”走进家门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛你就会用温柔的笑容来迎接我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.20,0:16:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是事与愿违 你已经不在人世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.40,0:16:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你尝尝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这次做得更好吃了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.30,0:17:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不会忘记你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.90,0:17:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论今后发生什么 我绝对不会忘记你的温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.80,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决不会忘记 你赐于我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.40,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请永远守望着我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我深爱的人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椰子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了没事的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.10,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是被我的演技所打动了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.00,0:17:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.00,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我确实有一点被感动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦想 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于近卫学姐而言 戏剧就是梦想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椰子也应该有类似的 梦想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说过这样的事很孩子气呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能问你一个问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的梦想为什么是戏剧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你问我为什么 这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.20,0:18:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和 和那个家伙完全无关啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是自言自语而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是能让其他人高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是为了让和美与妈妈都高兴啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.20,0:18:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我所感受到的欢乐和幸福传递给其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言 这就是戏剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 有人能因此而高兴的话便是最好不过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本就是这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.90,0:19:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有点帅过头了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 假如对方没有高兴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.80,0:19:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 又想吵架吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.80,0:19:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明有千言万语在心头 却始终无法传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 实在太可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椰子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.70,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那很简单啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在对方高兴之前一直努力就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.00,0:19:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始都不会很顺利 这是肯定的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近卫学姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一开始时也很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.40,0:19:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为有人在为我加油 在背后支持着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才能把梦想一直坚持下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.90,0:19:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.70,0:20:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 还是没法做得和爸爸一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢熟悉就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.10,0:20:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和美肯定能做出一手好菜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.00,0:20:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且比起前一阵有很大进步 非常了不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在笑什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.30,0:20:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我和那家伙没什么关系啦 况且那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学姐你可真是单纯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这算是在夸我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.70,0:20:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她到底是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.80,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给妈妈：
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.50,0:21:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是学生会执行部的返校日 我去学校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.70,0:21:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃的话 请尝尝早饭吧 ——和美留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.70,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸的味道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.60,0:21:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 良良 和美她人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她联络我们说会晚点过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.70,0:21:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.00,0:21:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这一集我的出场镜头就这么点了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.60,0:21:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椰子她到底窜哪去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.70,0:21:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论荒野有多广阔 我也绝不沮丧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.50,0:22:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你赐予我勇气 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.80,0:22:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远走下去 走我所选择的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.40,0:22:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与你一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.60,0:22:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的可以吃这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.40,0:22:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个当然不是白食 要对味道做出评价哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.30,0:22:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 要我做什么都行啦 那我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.20,0:22:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.50,0:22:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃啊 最棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.70,0:22:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要评述得那么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.60,0:22:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.90,0:23:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也让我吃点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.90,0:23:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦 这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.20,0:23:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大…大萝卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.00,0:25:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然咖喱里还要数萝卜咖喱最好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.10,0:25:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么又偷懒了 小螃蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.65,0:25:08.60,Default,,0000,0010,0075,,{\fad(300,0)\fs28\1c&ff0000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\bord2}打工充满了危险的芳香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.20,0:25:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.60,0:12:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 罗密欧 你为什么是罗密欧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时是恋爱中的少女朱丽叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.60,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时是离开花生便不能生存的名侦探 夏洛克.素奈绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时是为了复仇而举起大刀的女子高生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.70,0:12:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时是恋上王子的人鱼公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.90,0:12:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时是打倒恶魔女王的传说中的女剑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.80,0:12:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时是真心爱上朱丽叶的青年罗密欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.00,0:12:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时是被邪恶组织改造后的Rider素奈绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.60,0:12:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时还是穿着象征永恒爱情的纯白婚纱的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的真面目是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.50,0:13:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戏剧同好会的近卫素奈绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.90,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想来当一回“千面女郎”吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.50,0:13:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戏剧同好会 大批招收新成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.60,0:13:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诸位 加入戏剧同好会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.00,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,详情请咨询2－A的近卫素奈绪

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.57,0:13:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}西崎纪子的One Point Message

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家下午好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.40,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是西崎纪子的One Point Message时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.00,0:13:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正月里 装饰在大门前的门松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.00,0:13:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}门松：日本人贺岁迎新的吉祥物，材料多为松、竹、梅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.20,0:13:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其竹子的切口为什么要故意开在竹节处呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.80,0:13:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样弄的切口看起来像一张笑脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.90,0:13:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种毫不造作的自然笑容才配称为“演技”呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.50,0:13:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 诸位 回头见
